verses:
Amazing grace! How sweet the sound!
{translation}That saved a wretch like me!{/translation}
I once was lost, but now am found;
{translation}Was blind, but now I see.{/translation}

[end]
{translation}When we've been there ten thousand years,{/translation}
Bright shining as the sun,
{translation}We've no less days to sing God's praise,{/translation}
Than when we first begun.
